reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 31, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Super cute! Great find!
reviews.reviewText: I purchased the Emerald color in XS (I'm 5'4" and a lean 120 lbs). The fit is so flattering! The pants are a little long on me, and the bra top is little tight (I'm a 34C) but it works and is very supportive, even for HIIT/Burst training. The waist is high so you can get away wearing it without a shirt over top but I'm not quite that confident. I would purchase again in another color!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 7, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Love the fit!
reviews.reviewText: This set is so cute and you really can’t beat it for the price! It fits very snuggly and is ribbed which adds a little more flair. The color is vibrant and the fabric is thick and slimming. For reference I’m 5’3” 105lbs, 32C and k ordered an XS which fit perfectly.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 29, 2024
reviews.reviewText: This is a really cute set, I was just hoping for a darker red. Anyway, the set feels soft against my skin, has nice stretch and holds me in.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 19, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Very comfortable and stylish
reviews.reviewText: I was impressed by the quality, especially at this price point. The fabric was very soft, and the ribbed design is so cute. They felt very supportive, and held up through my barre workout. I am usually a large in sports bras and medium in leggings. I went with the medium and loved the fit on both.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 29, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars True to size
reviews.reviewText: For reference, I am 44 yrs old, 5'8", measurements 36-30-38, 36D and 140 lbs. I ordered the medium. As you can see these are full length. For us tall girls a big YES. Has great compression for the days you need it. The top is medium to high intensity support, but not crush your ribs tight. The girls stay in place. And can we just talk about the cut out in the top. Sexy, holds you in all the right ways. Bottoms are not actually sheer. Squat proof (sorry about my butt in your face) you can see the outline of my underwear but not the color. The compression works best with seamless, thong or no underwear. Does NOT ride up! If you order up it won't show the seam of your underwear so bad. But that's when you decide what kind of workout you want it for. Or do you care if the seam shows.There is NO camel toe issues what so ever. Doesn't slide down, stays put. Very high waisted and stretchy. I had room to pull it up to my bra. Thick but breathable material. Did I say great compression? It is snug, not tight. But you are sinched in nice and comfy. Amazing for high intensity workouts.This color is bright and fun. My bathroom light doesn't do it justice. Soft and ribbed material, but I don't forsee pilling to be an issue. So all being said with my measurements the medium fits perfect for my high intensity days. If you want more of a yoga relaxed fit then order a size up. I need these in every color. If you are in between sizes and want compression order down, relaxed order up.This is a sexy little number. It doesn't do my flat butt any justice and flattens the girls a little but I don't care. It is functional and comfortable. Ladies, new to working out or a pro this is a must get set and the price is worth it for this quality. Did I mention no camel toe, lol. When I do a sweaty workout I will update if shows sweat puddles or wicks away. I blame #hopescope for this great pick!Don't think anymore! Get it!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 27, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Super Cute, but Beige is see through
reviews.reviewText: Snug fit, not too tight! I am 5’7” and 140 lbs, I am a small for a top but medium for bottoms. I went for a medium and this set fits perfectly. I consider myself small chested but the top made my boobs look great! The ribbing is really nice. BUT I got the Beige color and it’s definitely see through for the leggings. Does NOT pass the squat test, even without the squat test you see it all. Also, the leggings do give me camel toe, I noticed some reviews said that they didn’t, maybe they got a darker color so it’s not noticeable? Since I mostly workout at home, I’m not going to bother with returning this set, because I still think it’s super cute. I can still wear the top out in the world, but the leggings are for home only. Perhaps I will consider getting a different color.
